{"tid":1681580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：支持警隊 “依法止暴”.  PoPo 自己睇路啦","createTime":"2019-10-29T13:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T13:58:43.000Z","uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bd31e9d1e752b9d209dbfcf474f5c404b4fd7aa4","tid":1681580,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:51:16.000Z","msg":"特首冀各界勿為少數暴徒找藉口　必須支持警隊依法止暴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥形容，暴徒無日無之找尋藉口，進行極端暴力行為，她希望社會各界不要為少數暴徒的行為提供合理化藉口。她又說過去4個多月，社會出現不實的指控，或對警員有不公平攻擊，重申必須支持警隊依法止暴。<br />\n<br />\n對於有外國媒體報道，中央有意撤換她，林鄭月娥說，外交部早前已澄清，指報道是別有用心的謠言，又說中央政府一直以來都支持她作為特首，處理現時的暴力事件。"},{"pid":"138cba78d809e62a5862dbdb15d1edfa3e7e0dff","tid":1681580,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:51:36.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e9519dcc1aac8e1652c778ff697807c3c11c79","tid":1681580,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488786-20191029.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488786-20191029.htm&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=e6f41ad7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488786-20191029.htm&h=99c335c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488786-20191029.htm</a>"},{"pid":"48bb283113ba6430f43219b7ec06836d9758048f","tid":1681580,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"口風月月唔同 證明開始準備清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9664ccda3f960f50187cd51b7a7e643ea06da328","tid":1681580,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep